<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased API Error Rates>
We are investigating increased API error rates and launch failures in the US-WEST-2 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased API Error Rates>
Between 12:29 PM and 12:56 PM PDT, we experienced increased API error rates and launch failures in the US-WEST-2 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
